<HEAD>The Poultry.</HEAD>

<argument><p><list type=toc>

<ITEM>The Early Home of the London Poulterers</ITEM>

<ITEM>Its Mysterious Desertion</ITEM>

<ITEM>Noteworthy Sites in the Poultry</ITEM>

<ITEM>The Birthplace of Tom Hood, Senior</ITEM>

<ITEM>A Pretty Quarrel at the Rose Tavern</ITEM>

<ITEM>A Costly Sign-board</ITEM>

<ITEM>The <num value="3">Three</num> Cranes</ITEM>

<ITEM>The Home of the Dillys</ITEM>

<ITEM>Johnsoniana</ITEM>

<ITEM>St. Mildred's Church, Poultry</ITEM>

<ITEM>Quaint Epitaphs</ITEM>

<ITEM>The Poultry Compter</ITEM>

<ITEM>Attack on Dr. Lamb, the Conjurer</ITEM>

<ITEM>Dekker, the Dramatist</ITEM>

<ITEM>Ned Ward's Description of the Compter</ITEM>

